  m_Name: Step3_Axles
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EngineNarrationStep
  stepLabel: MAIN BEARINGS
  narrationText: "These are the main bearing journals \u2014 what you called the
    crankshaft axles.\n\nThey support the crankshaft at multiple points along its
    length, preventing flex and vibration.\n\nIn a real engine, these surfaces are
    lubricated with pressurized oil. Without them, the crankshaft would destroy itself
    within seconds."
  voiceOver: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 627105df1ced10a499cb85aba6a6f3e2, type: 3}
